reviewText: Get an inside look at the hottest church planting training available in DVD form. A video tour by one of the three trainers, Brian Hogan, author of There's a Sheep in my Bathtub: Birth of a Mongolian Church Planting Movement.

In this video I review and introduce this DVD training seminar for church planting. I am one of the three trainers featured in the product and the author of There's a Sheep in my Bathtub: Birth of a Mongolian Church Planting Movement
